BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION
The denominators are already the same--add the numerators and simplify if possible.

[``\frac{[$num1]}{[$den]}``]

We can factor the numerator:

[``\frac{[$num2]}{[$den]}``]

And cancel out the common factor:

[``[$f]``]


